{"tid":1155158,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足鍾意vaporwave","createTime":"2019-05-14T18:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T10:12:27.000Z","uid":143093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a00c2514c93ffdd417cc03e97dd21a22deefa5b0","tid":1155158,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T18:27:16.000Z","msg":"貼啲經典嘅出嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aQkPcPqTq4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaQkPcPqTq4M&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=371a4a84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aQkPcPqTq4M</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ki-fATpXa00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKi-fATpXa00&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=33b773d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ki-fATpXa00</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OrR1TGQY20Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOrR1TGQY20Y&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=5b4fc8ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OrR1TGQY20Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ULfFe9_D1c&amp;t=6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9ULfFe9_D1c%26t%3D6s&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=d1bf0dce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ULfFe9_D1c&amp;t=6s</a>"},{"pid":"7b6ff8e2b191370cd32bb1e3f7351202f6aab48b","tid":1155158,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T18:29:43.000Z","msg":"俾返少少資料先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蒸氣波（英語：Vaporwave，或作蒸汽波）是一種電子音樂類型，出現於2010年初的網際網路社區，隨後逐漸從網絡模因發展成為了藝術運動。這類作品側重於20世紀80年代、90年代的美國、日本流行文化元素，包括城市生活、購物中心、商業廣告、電子遊戲、科技和早期網際網路等，也受到賽博龐克科幻的影響。其音樂大量使用同時代的沙發音樂、滑順爵士樂、電梯音樂等商業音樂作為素材，進行採樣和編輯。[2][6][7]《Vice》的米歇爾&middot;洛克（Michelle Lhooq）表示，即使蒸氣波的素材來自「糟糕」、「垃圾」的商業音樂，但蒸氣波並不是為了模仿或者重新創作商業音樂，而是把商業音樂變成「更性感」的合成音樂。參與者將蒸氣波的風格稱為「美學」，為了與自身風格一致，常使用全角字符寫作ＡＥＳＴＨＥＴＩＣＳ。<br />\n<br />\n蒸氣波表現出了對資本主義、消費主義和全球化一種模稜兩可的反思。一方面，有評論者認為蒸氣波是反資本主義和反消費主義的，以反諷的手法對其進行批判；同時也有評論認為，蒸氣波體現出對昔日繁榮社會的懷舊情懷，表現出復古未來主義。而個人電腦和影音娛樂等科技元素，喚起了人們的文化記憶，以及昔日烏托邦主義遠景破滅的嘆息；而《布魯克林鐵路》雜誌的一篇評論則表示，蒸氣波表達了對當下政治失敗和社會異化的不滿，但與龐克搖滾的那種「原始的能量」相比，蒸氣波則側重於被動的接受，表現出失落和委靡不振的情緒。"},{"pid":"9a7d64909f644d5dc407130866f70db1a1a2392d","tid":1155158,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"間唔中tunein聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fbb6e6c96e099001eee3242d11aaa4fa3ecae7","tid":1155158,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"唔計Macintosh Plus同Chuck Person's eccojams vol. 1兩隻神枱級<br />\n最鍾意應該係佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QudRchF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQudRchF.png&h=0ce33d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nv i r t u a l r e s o r t &trade; - CYBEREALITYライフ<br />\n<a href=\"https://cybereality90.bandcamp.com/album/v-i-r-t-u-a-l-r-e-s-o-r-t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcybereality90.bandcamp.com%2Falbum%2Fv-i-r-t-u-a-l-r-e-s-o-r-t&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=8a800275\" target=\"_blank\">https://cybereality90.bandcamp.com/album/v-i-r-t-u-a-l-r-e-s-o-r-t</a><br />\n<br />\n之後就係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQaDBMs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQaDBMs.png&h=281a2b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSplit LP - Mensa Group International / luxury elite<br />\n<a href=\"https://ailanthusrecordings.bandcamp.com/album/split-lp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Failanthusrecordings.bandcamp.com%2Falbum%2Fsplit-lp&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgV04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=0e57